description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'Level Up Your Cadence | 10 Minute Cycling Workout' from the channel GCN Training.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: In this short and sweet workout, Manon will work on some cadence drills with you to improve your ability and comfort when pedalling quickly. The big efforts are done at over 100 rpm and the session varies in intensity throughout!

Session breakdown:
2 mins @ 2/10 (80 rpm)
30 mins @ 6/10 (100 rpm)
30 mins @ 8/10 (110 rpm)
2 mins @ 2/10 (80 rpm)
30 mins @ 6/10 (100 rpm)
30 mins @ 8/10 (110 rpm)
30 mins @ 10/10 (120 rpm)
1 mins @ 6/10 (80 rpm)
30 mins @ 8/10 (100 rpm)
30 mins @ 10/10 (110 rpm)
30 mins @ 10/10 (120 rpm)
1 mins @ 1/10 (80 rpm)
